@page
@model FinEd.Views.Home.PensionPages.PensionSection2Model
@{

}
<div class="pension-benefits">
    <h2>Benefits of Pensions</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Provides financial security in retirement.</li>
        <li>Many pensions are tax-advantaged, meaning you can save on taxes.</li>
        <li>Potential employer contributions in workplace pensions.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="pension-contributions">
    <h2>Pension Contributions</h2>
    <p>
        It's important to regularly contribute to your pension throughout your working life. Contributions may come from your salary, your employer, and government incentives.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="pension-planning">
    <h2>Pension Planning</h2>
    <p>
        Proper planning is crucial to ensure you have enough income to support your lifestyle in retirement. Consider factors like your desired retirement age, lifestyle, and any other income sources.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="pension-faq">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>How much should I contribute to my pension?</strong> It depends on your income, retirement goals, and age. A financial advisor can help you determine the best amount.</li>
        <li><strong>When can I access my pension?</strong> This depends on the type of pension you have. Generally, pensions can be accessed from age 55, but this may vary.</li>
        <li><strong>What happens to my pension if I change jobs?</strong> You can usually transfer your workplace pension to your new employer's scheme or a personal pension.</li>
    </ul>
    
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <!-- Question 2 -->
    <div class="quiz-question">
        <h3>2. Which of the following is NOT a type of pension?</h3>
        <div>
            <input type="radio" id="q2a" name="q2" value="a">
            <label for="q2a">State Pension</label>
        </div>
        <div>
            <input type="radio" id="q2b" name="q2" value="b">
            <label for="q2b">Workplace Pension</label>
        </div>
        <div>
            <input type="radio" id="q2c" name="q2" value="c">
            <label for="q2c">Investment Pension</label>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary mt-2" onclick="checkAnswers()">Submit Answer</button>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="PensionSection3">Next</a>
</div>

<style>
    .btn {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #2C3E50;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
</style>

<script>
    function checkAnswers() {
        const answer = document.querySelector('input[name="q2"]:checked');

        if (answer && answer.value === "c") {
            alert("Correct! Investment Pension is not a standard type of pension.");
        } else {
            alert("Incorrect. Please review the types of pensions and try again.");
        }
    }
</script>
